Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.97,0:17:02.11,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}私を導く
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.36,0:17:08.49,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}遠い遠い呼び声よ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.86,0:17:12.32,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}微笑むように
