Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.70,0:02:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.45,0:02:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  猪尾吕义先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.91,0:02:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们终于来到这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类们所居住的人间  明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.13,0:02:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.36,0:02:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始要看你努力的程度来决定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.51,0:02:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否可以实现你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.30,0:02:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个你应该明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.23,0:02:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  当然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.17,0:03:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你知道了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.67,0:03:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么刚一到这里就钻进这个窄窄的鬼地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.55,0:03:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是但是  总觉得这样藏起来商量事情很有神秘感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.91,0:03:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也很开心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你开心有什么用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.72,0:03:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花户小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.17,0:03:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的愿望是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.29,0:03:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有个想去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.50,0:03:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了实现这个目的你须要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.36,0:03:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须用「瓶子」收集很多受伤的心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.45,0:03:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这之前呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.93,0:03:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须得到这个「瓶子」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了得到「瓶子」要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.44,0:03:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须在测试能否在这里生活的考试中合格
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.27,0:03:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.53,0:03:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一整天你要在人间生活  以此来考验你的常识
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.49,0:03:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考试已经开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.49,0:03:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在本大爷的监视和裁判下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.94,0:04:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白了没  混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.43,0:04:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考试是以你按照这里的常识来行动的程度来判定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.02,0:04:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  做给我看吧  小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.94,0:04:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,符合在春天的公园里的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.94,0:04:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  猪尾吕义先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是春眠的蓑虫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.56,0:04:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  在公园都没办法正常的行动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.54,0:04:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.98,0:04:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是的  为什么没帮我把垃圾扔掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.89,0:04:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶不上公车了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.34,0:05:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.63,0:05:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.48,0:05:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌  要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猪尾吕义先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉在地上了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好  下一个考试来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.79,0:05:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看你要怎么处理这包垃圾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.10,0:05:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.10,0:05:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,垃圾堆…垃圾堆在…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.12,0:05:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.22,0:05:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.47,0:05:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.56,0:05:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.97,0:05:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请尽量减少垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌鸦先生们…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.23,0:05:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盯着那包垃圾呢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.19,0:06:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不快点就要被它们啄了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.99,0:06:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌鸦先生们…盯着…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,垃圾…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.53,0:06:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌鸦先生们  请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.80,0:06:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫乌鸦过来是什么意思啊  混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌鸦先生的肚子饿了 那边又写着「请减少垃圾」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不叫小鸠  叫土鸠就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.72,0:06:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.16,0:06:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.36,0:06:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在一个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.20,0:07:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去喝杯茶怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.14,0:07:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝茶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.13,0:07:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这附近有家不错的店
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.15,0:07:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  光天化日之下搭讪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.35,0:07:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们请客
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.81,0:07:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请客？谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.06,0:07:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了  猪尾吕义先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.61,0:07:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来这里是做什么的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.40,0:07:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有人请客…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.94,0:07:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.87,0:07:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里受伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋  你刚才做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  不要小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.17,0:07:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  原来有男人了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.83,0:08:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…谢谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.44,0:08:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要被人奉承就飘飘然起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有飘飘然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.15,0:08:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  你都开心成那样了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.41,0:08:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也难怪他会那么想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.04,0:08:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是个大晴天  真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.63,0:08:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赏花的客人也很多  会变得很忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.36,0:08:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  藤本
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.84,0:08:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这个拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.28,0:08:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是只很可爱的猫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.43,0:08:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的盘子我收走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.55,0:08:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.84,0:09:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.42,0:09:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  要问问他的名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.86,0:09:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问问嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是不亲切呢  藤本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.57,0:09:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只要多笑笑就会很受欢迎的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.37,0:09:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  不受欢迎也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.85,0:09:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个不可爱的家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  忘记关机了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾草托儿所
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.81,0:09:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  我是藤本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.56,0:09:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  清花老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.16,0:09:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人又跑到托儿所…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.66,0:09:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我一下  我马上就去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.73,0:09:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  店长  有点急事…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.43,0:09:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事啊  有好多人聚集在这里呢  猪尾吕义先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么赏花的庙会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.90,0:10:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过话说回来  这味道还真香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.62,0:10:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.30,0:10:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是  去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱花盛开呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.41,0:10:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  扔过来下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.92,0:10:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.49,0:10:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我扔了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.43,0:10:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.39,0:10:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  怎么了怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.65,0:10:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.41,0:10:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.93,0:10:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.11,0:10:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就人手不足…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.07,0:10:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.48,0:10:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为赔礼  请让我帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追加一瓶啤酒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.51,0:11:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  打工的刚巧回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.05,0:11:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.94,0:11:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗  能帮上您的忙我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对小鸠来说还真是稀奇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  这边的火锅还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.24,0:11:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.35,0:11:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有听我说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.68,0:11:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在听呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.99,0:11:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  可以帮我煮一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.15,0:11:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.64,0:11:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来…煮火锅…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.86,0:11:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个也可以作为考试啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.34,0:11:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我见识一下吧  小鸠煮火锅的手艺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.93,0:12:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水没烧开不可以放进去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.97,0:12:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  还不能放肉…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  为什么要加牛奶…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.99,0:12:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有营养…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.49,0:12:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煮巧克力就免了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.02,0:12:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多吃甜食能让人更有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.78,0:12:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放纳豆啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.07,0:12:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像地狱图绘一样呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.57,0:12:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不过…不吃又太浪费了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.63,0:12:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.47,0:12:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.23,0:12:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.49,0:12:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板也来尝尝看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.89,0:12:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.14,0:13:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.57,0:13:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.65,0:13:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真美味
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘  我会把这个作为店里的招牌菜的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.73,0:13:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.33,0:13:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么年轻却很能干呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.97,0:13:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞得连我都想吃吃看了啊  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.58,0:13:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区土鸠还真是嚣张呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.42,0:13:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才小鸠  在火锅的常识上是0分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.21,0:13:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.54,0:13:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  结果上来看火锅还算好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.95,0:13:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就给你个40分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.24,0:13:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜  怎么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.25,0:13:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖  飞喽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.13,0:14:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子总是哭个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.89,0:14:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是小姑娘的错  别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.49,0:14:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子  一到晚上总是会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.05,0:14:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不给邻居添麻烦  我经常带他到这个公园里来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.04,0:14:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他不哭到累了是不会睡觉的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.62,0:14:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.42,0:14:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前他母亲总是陪在他身边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.03,0:14:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要这孩子一哭就一定会唱歌给他听
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.44,0:14:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哄他到不哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.17,0:14:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他妈妈  现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.15,0:15:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时间她正为了这孩子努力地工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.80,0:15:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这孩子必须由我来好好照看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.36,0:15:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  听了奶奶唱的歌他也还是哭个不停呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.88,0:15:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我来唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.82,0:15:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了这个孩子  请让我来唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.93,0:15:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然或许无法唱得像这孩子的妈妈一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.73,0:15:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以拜托你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.34,0:15:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.20,0:15:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会努力唱的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.18,0:16:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  我现在已经回到打工的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.34,0:16:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老师不必在意…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.88,0:16:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  有歌声…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠也就只有唱歌拿手了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.43,0:17:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  这点琥珀也是一样的么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.01,0:17:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.69,0:18:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常动听哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.92,0:18:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子好像也不哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.63,0:18:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.60,0:18:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了小姑娘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.73,0:18:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  再让我听一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.85,0:18:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多唱几首吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.84,0:18:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有舞台  去那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.82,0:18:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.63,0:18:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到了很多大家送的礼物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.40,0:18:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然说是唱歌的谢礼  那收下也可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.81,0:18:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.02,0:19:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个那个  考试呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.34,0:19:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  考试呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.93,0:19:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花户小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.35,0:19:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.83,0:19:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前半场你尽做些傻事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.66,0:19:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后半的那个火锅也是偶然的产物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.07,0:19:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌倒是还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.33,0:19:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.73,0:19:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不合格
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才不是说了歌还是不错的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.26,0:19:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前半太废了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分  太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.53,0:19:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是很努力了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.98,0:19:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过也是刚巧不及格  真遗憾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.50,0:19:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.56,0:19:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的老奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.68,0:19:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好  歌声动听的小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.03,0:19:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能再见到你真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才真是太谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想来向你道声谢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.08,0:20:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子听了母亲以外的歌声后那么高兴还是第一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.80,0:20:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是刚以为他心情变好了  他却马上又睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.78,0:20:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你特意为了我的孙子唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.92,0:20:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我却连句谢谢都没说就回去了  真是抱歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.27,0:20:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不用了  不敢当
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的歌声真的很动听哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.69,0:20:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次请再让我听听吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.56,0:20:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.29,0:20:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.74,0:20:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.62,0:21:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花户小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.75,0:21:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.30,0:21:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合格了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.16,0:21:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.62,0:21:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「瓶子」…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.83,0:21:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.19,0:21:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.92,0:21:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  有了刚才那个老奶奶的感谢  所以100分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.62,0:21:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考试合格了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.75,0:21:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.80,0:21:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要的话就还给我！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.93,0:22:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要我要！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.05,0:22:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治愈受伤的心  将心的碎片装满这个「瓶子」的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.82,0:22:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿望就会实现
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.26,0:22:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你还只是刚得到了瓶子而已呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.13,0:22:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.31,0:22:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花户小鸠  你的愿望是？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.58,0:22:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有个想去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.00,0:22:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了实现这个目的你须要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.77,0:22:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须用「瓶子」收集很多受伤的心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.87,0:22:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好  接下来才真正的开始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.87,0:22:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走的路还远得很呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.88,0:22:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.01,0:22:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.10,0:22:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘻嘻哈哈的  真的明白了吗  土鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.00,0:22:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！ 太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.09,0:22:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是小鸠  花户小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.42,0:22:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土鸠就足够了  不愿意的话就斑鸠好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.26,0:22:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？ 斑鸠？
